{"tid":1944414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"早於2019年12月31日，《人民日報》已經率先採用「武漢肺炎」","createTime":"2020-03-26T11:03:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T04:59:29.000Z","uid":41998,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9c9569252857b24212b2fc9782d7540d874f8b2e","tid":1944414,"uid":41998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T11:03:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HTR1xBD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHTR1xBD.jpg&h=6fe4724d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【#又真係白紙黑字 #所以美方都冇抵賴 #照直講 #話時話都係跟你講 #又不爽】中國 #外交部 發言人 #耿爽 早兩日指，近期 #武肺 源頭的爭論是由美方挑起，是美方首先稱病毒起源於中國。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽仲煞有介事指出美國國務卿 Michael Pompeo (蓬佩奧) 早喺今年 3月6日 就已經叫武肺做「#武漢病毒」。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽：白紙黑字，言猶在耳，美方是抵賴不了！<br />\n<br />\n都唔使翻查資料，上一上微博，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>搵一搵《#人民日報》，就會見到 2019年12月31日，《人民日報》已經率先採用「#武漢肺炎」。白紙黑字，真係冇得抵賴。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n《人民日報》#Weibo<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4455530086650043\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.weibo.cn%2Fstatus%2F4455530086650043&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR%2FGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=485b6a0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.weibo.cn/status/4455530086650043</a><br />\n<br />\n《#香港電台》源頭爭論報導：<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1516538-20200324.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1516538-20200324.htm&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR%2FGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=e7fa6e2e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1516538-20200324.htm&h=74a33ac3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1516538-20200324.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n《#香港電台》耿爽指美國浪費時間報導：<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1516343-20200323.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1516343-